{"tid":2206494,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人越大，老豆越似廢老","createTime":"2020-09-17T13:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T18:21:58.000Z","uid":372637,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"47b410f56acfcb26ee4b1f7d06b81e4593a3e2f6","tid":2206494,"uid":372637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"細細個望老豆又高又大隻，成個超人咁，會喺度諗大個一定要搵啲好似老豆咁嘅男人結婚<br />\n但係慢慢老豆啲劣根性就露出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人又懶又唔識用下腦<br />\n好普通一件事例如計下數，唔想心算咪用計數機囉，佢連算計數機數懶，一係搵我幫，再唔係就搵老母<br />\n又例如叫佢搞網上銀行，佢又唔肯搞又唔講原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就連寫個字，睇一封信都要我地幫佢<br />\n究竟由幾時開始出咗問題，定佢一直都係咁...."},{"pid":"259f6503ecc36504317722407f26220b82aa20f5","tid":2206494,"uid":336645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:33:12.000Z","msg":"有冇叫雞"},{"pid":"2129010c68d494a98d38910238b2cef1ae07ba38","tid":2206494,"uid":355310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"算啦，第日自己老左咪又係咁，盡量幫下佢啦"},{"pid":"9e6c9d01bb94a8991cda515688b6ff2cf8d8f79d","tid":2206494,"uid":372637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"259f6503ecc36504317722407f26220b82aa20f5","tid":2206494,"uid":336645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:33:12.000Z","msg":"有冇叫雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:34:47.000Z","msg":"應該冇掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢日日放工就打電話返屋企話佢返嚟<br />\n去買嘢都會講聲"},{"pid":"7c82c12270022aa183d6bd821fcc807fdb81be70","tid":2206494,"uid":61030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"可能係你大個咗冇咩點同佢溝通<br />\n佢借啲意同你講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af4b34a428f5f78407b73e018d9